Rating: 3
Easy to make, great to prepare ahead, very tasty party food which does look terrific, a keeper

Rating: 4
I make this every year for New Year's Day brunch for friends -- about 50 -- and NEVER have any leftovers even when triple or quadruple the recipe. Deliciously tangy with just enough piquancy from the peppers. Not only does it look great, but it's a breeze to make.